# GPU-fit tuning: Qwen3-Coder-Next Q5_K_M on Strix Halo (MACHINE=strixhalo).
#
# Sourced by the launchers AFTER models/qwen3-coder-next.env and BEFORE
# profiles/strixhalo/default.env. Holds only what depends on fitting this model's
# ~56 GiB of weights on Strix Halo's unified memory.
#
# N_CPU_MOE keeps this many MoE expert layers in CPU/system RAM. On unified memory
# the GPU still reaches them, freeing GTT for the dense layers + a big KV cache.
# 40 is a good start; lower it (more on GPU) if you have headroom, raise it if OOM.
# We emit the --n-cpu-moe flag HERE (not in the model env) because the offload
# amount is a property of THIS card's memory, not of the model.
: "${N_CPU_MOE:=40}"
LLAMA_ARGS+=(--n-cpu-moe "${N_CPU_MOE}")
